snippet.textDisplay:
If you want to take surveyors more quietly and loot everything at once without picking up armor plates as they fall off from the damage AND if you have some time - just follow it in stealth for some time, keep about 30-40m distance from them and wait for Surveyors to chill out and open up - revealing a laser beam. Hit that spot with Ferro, it will roll away and will have to open up again after some time. Repeat it  5-7 times and you will get it as well.

This might not be optimal if you'd rather use a wolfpack, but this is a good tactic for someone who's playing the game for the first few hours
